msgstr "신용 카드 상환 계산기, 부채 상환, 부채 눈덩이, 부채 눈사태, 신용 카드이자, 부채 상환"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate how to pay off credit card debt faster."
msgstr "신용카드 빚을 더 빨리 갚는 방법을 계산해보세요."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:37
msgid ""
"See how long it will take to pay off your credit card debt and how much "
