msgstr "ROI란 무엇입니까?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:35
msgid ""
"ROI (Return on Investment) measures how much profit or loss your investment "
"generates relative to its cost, expressed as a percentage."
msgstr "ROI(투자 수익률)는 투자 비용 대비 수익 또는 손실이 얼마나 되는지를 백분율로 표시합니다."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:73
