#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:301
msgid "Add any regular monthly contributions you plan to make."
msgstr "정기적으로 매월 기부할 계획을 추가하세요."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/investment_calculator.html:307
msgid "Set Parameters"
