msgstr "필수 최소 배포판 없음"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:348
msgid ""
"Unlike Traditional IRAs, Roth IRAs have no RMDs during your lifetime, giving"
" you more control."
msgstr "기존 IRA와 달리 Roth IRA는 평생 동안 RMD가 없으므로 더 많은 통제권을 제공합니다."

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/roth_ira_calculator.html:356
