msgstr "프로 운동선수, 매우 활동적"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:443
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:474
