msgstr "결과를 보려면 'BMR 계산'을 클릭하세요."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/bmr_calculator.html:446
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/tdee_calculator.html:456
