msgstr "생리주기 계산기, 생리주기 계산기, 생리주기 계산기, 배란일 계산기, 가임기"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:15
msgid "Track your menstrual cycle and predict your next period dates."
msgstr "생리 주기를 추적하고 다음 생리 날짜를 예측하세요."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:24
msgid "Track menstrual cycle and predict next period dates"
msgstr "생리 주기를 추적하고 다음 생리 날짜를 예측하세요"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Track your menstrual cycle and predict your next period dates, ovulation, "
"and fertile window. Get comprehensive cycle analysis and personalized "
"predictions."
msgstr "생리 주기를 추적하고 다음 생리일, 배란 및 가임기를 예측하세요. 포괄적인 주기 분석과 맞춤형 예측을 얻으세요."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:73
msgid "Last Period Start Date"
msgstr "마지막 기간 시작일"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:94
msgid "Period Length"
msgstr "기간"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:101
msgid "Range: 2-7 days (average: 5 days)"
msgstr "범위: 2~7일(평균: 5일)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:145
msgid ""
"Enter your cycle information to see predictions for your next periods, "
"ovulation dates, fertile windows, and comprehensive cycle analysis."
msgstr "생리 주기 정보를 입력하여 다음 생리 기간, 배란일, 가임기 및 포괄적인 주기 분석에 대한 예측을 확인하세요."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:168
#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:372
msgid "Current Cycle Day"
msgstr "현재 주기일"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:175
msgid "Days Until Period"
msgstr "기간까지 남은 일수"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:181
msgid "Days Until Ovulation"
msgstr "배란일까지 남은 일수"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/period_calculator.html:193
