#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your target heart rate zones for different training intensities. "
"Includes Karvonen method and standard formulas."
msgstr "다양한 훈련 강도에 대한 목표 심박수 영역을 계산합니다. Karvonen 방법과 표준 공식이 포함되어 있습니다."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"target heart rate calculator, heart rate zones, karvonen method, training "
"zones, max heart rate"
msgstr "목표 심박수 계산기, 심박수 구역, 카르보넨 방법, 훈련 구역, 최대 심박수"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:15
msgid "Calculate your target heart rate zones for optimal training."
msgstr "최적의 훈련을 위해 목표 심박수 구간을 계산하세요."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate target heart rate zones for training"
msgstr "훈련을 위한 목표 심박수 구역 계산"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your target heart rate zones for different training intensities. "
"Includes Karvonen method and standard formulas for optimal training."
msgstr ""
"다양한 훈련 강도에 대한 목표 심박수 영역을 계산합니다. 최적의 훈련을 위한 Karvonen 방법과 표준 공식이 포함되어 있습니다."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/target_heart_rate_calculator.html:77
