#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:292
msgid "Calculate confidence interval"
msgstr "신뢰 구간 계산"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:296
msgid "Calculate Confidence Interval"
msgstr "신뢰 구간 계산"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:340
msgid ""
"Enter your data to calculate the confidence interval for population mean or "
"proportion."
msgstr "모집단 평균 또는 비율에 대한 신뢰 구간을 계산하려면 데이터를 입력하세요."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:350
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:424
msgid "Confidence Interval"
msgstr "신뢰구간"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:397
msgid "What is a Confidence Interval?"
msgstr "신뢰 구간이란 무엇입니까?"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:399
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A confidence interval is a range of values that is likely to contain the "
"true population parameter with a specified level of confidence. For example,"
" a 95%% confidence interval means we are 95%% confident that the true "
"population parameter lies within the calculated range."
msgstr ""
"신뢰 구간은 지정된 신뢰 수준을 갖는 실제 모집단 매개변수를 포함할 가능성이 있는 값의 범위입니다. 예를 들어, 95%% 신뢰 구간은 "
"실제 모집단 매개변수가 계산된 범위 내에 있다고 95%% 신뢰한다는 의미입니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:402
msgid ""
"Confidence intervals are used in statistics to estimate population "
"parameters when we only have sample data."
msgstr "신뢰구간은 표본 데이터만 있을 때 모집단 모수를 추정하기 위해 통계에서 사용됩니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:410
msgid "Select calculation type: Mean or Proportion"
msgstr "계산 유형 선택: 평균 또는 비율"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:411
msgid ""
"Enter your sample data (mean/proportion, sample size, standard deviation for"
" mean)"
msgstr "표본 데이터 입력(평균/비율, 표본 크기, 평균의 표준 편차)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:412
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Select or enter your desired confidence level (90%%, 95%%, 99%%, or custom)"
msgstr "원하는 신뢰 수준(90%%, 95%%, 99%% 또는 사용자 정의)을 선택하거나 입력합니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:413
msgid ""
"For mean calculations, check if population standard deviation is known "
"(z-interval) or unknown (t-interval)"
msgstr "평균 계산의 경우 모집단 표준 편차가 알려져 있는지(z-구간) 또는 알 수 없는지(t-구간) 확인하세요."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:415
msgid "Review the results, visualizations, and detailed explanation"
msgstr "결과, 시각화 및 자세한 설명을 검토합니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:426
msgid ""
"The range of values that likely contains the true population parameter. For "
"example, [45.2, 54.8] means we are confident the true value lies between "
"45.2 and 54.8."
msgstr ""
"실제 모집단 매개변수가 포함될 가능성이 있는 값의 범위입니다. 예를 들어, [45.2, 54.8]은 실제 값이 45.2와 54.8 사이에"
" 있다고 확신한다는 의미입니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:430
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:774
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/sample_size_calculator.html:243
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/sample_size_calculator.html:330
msgid "Margin of Error"
msgstr "오차 한계"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:432
msgid ""
"Half the width of the confidence interval. It represents the maximum amount "
"by which the sample statistic may differ from the true population parameter."
msgstr "신뢰 구간 너비의 절반입니다. 이는 표본 통계가 실제 모집단 모수와 다를 수 있는 최대량을 나타냅니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:436
msgid "Z-Interval vs T-Interval"
msgstr "Z-간격과 T-간격"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:438
msgid ""
"Z-interval is used when population standard deviation is known. T-interval "
"is used when only sample standard deviation is known, accounting for "
"additional uncertainty."
msgstr ""
"Z-구간은 모집단 표준편차를 알 때 사용됩니다. T-구간은 표본 표준 편차만 알려진 경우 추가 불확실성을 고려하여 사용됩니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:449
msgid "Example 1: Mean Confidence Interval"
msgstr "예 1: 평균 신뢰 구간"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:450
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Sample Mean: 50, Sample Size: 100, Standard Deviation: 10, Confidence Level:"
" 95%%"
msgstr "표본 평균: 50, 표본 크기: 100, 표준 편차: 10, 신뢰 수준: 95%%"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:451
#, python-format
msgid "Result: 95%% CI = [48.04, 51.96]"
msgstr "결과: 95%% CI = [48.04, 51.96]"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:452
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Interpretation: We are 95%% confident the true population mean lies between "
"48.04 and 51.96."
msgstr "해석: 우리는 실제 모집단 평균이 48.04와 51.96 사이에 있다고 95%% 확신합니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:455
msgid "Example 2: Proportion Confidence Interval"
msgstr "예 2: 비율 신뢰 구간"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:456
#, python-format
msgid "Sample Proportion: 0.45, Sample Size: 200, Confidence Level: 95%%"
msgstr "표본 비율: 0.45, 표본 크기: 200, 신뢰 수준: 95%%"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:457
#, python-format
msgid "Result: 95%% CI = [0.381, 0.519]"
msgstr "결과: 95%% CI = [0.381, 0.519]"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:458
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Interpretation: We are 95%% confident the true population proportion lies "
"between 38.1%% and 51.9%%."
msgstr "해석: 우리는 실제 인구 비율이 38.1%%에서 51.9%% 사이에 있다고 95%% 확신합니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:471
msgid "Sample size must be at least 2 for valid calculations."
msgstr "유효한 계산을 위해서는 표본 크기가 2 이상이어야 합니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:477
msgid "For proportions, the value must be between 0 and 1."
msgstr "비율의 경우 값은 0에서 1 사이여야 합니다."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:483
msgid ""
"Larger sample sizes result in narrower confidence intervals (more precise "
"estimates)."
msgstr "표본 크기가 클수록 신뢰 구간이 좁아집니다(더 정확한 추정치)."

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/confidence_interval_calculator.html:489
msgid ""
"Higher confidence levels result in wider intervals (less precise but more "
"confident)."
msgstr "신뢰 수준이 높을수록 간격이 넓어집니다(정확성은 떨어지지만 신뢰도는 높아짐)."

